OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1780873386
OL,3,CContract signed with construction
OL,4,Cgiant to build Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FJersey's government has signed a
OL,7,Fcontract with the construction firm
OL,8,FBouygues UK to build the island's new
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FThe announcement comes two days before
OL,12,Fthe election, following months of
OL,13,Fnegotiation.
OL,15,F"The procurement process for the
OL,16,FOverdale Acute Hospital Main Works
OL,17,FContract has concluded," a statement
OL,18,Freleased by the Government under The
OL,19,FNew Healthcare Facilities Programme
OL,20,Fsays.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
