FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1780873386
OL,3,CContract signed with construction
OL,4,Cgiant to build Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FThey add that the deal is "within the
OL,7,Ffinancial envelope agreed by the
OL,8,FStates Assembly" - referring to the
OL,9,F#710 million project budget, which
OL,10,Fincludes two other "major sites" at
OL,11,Fthe Kensington Place ambulance
OL,12,Ffacility and St Saviour Health Village.
OL,14,FThe majority of the money will be
OL,15,Fspent on the new hospital, although
OL,16,Fthe Government will not confirm how
OL,17,Fmuch.
OL,19,FThe Health Minister, Deputy Tom Binet,
OL,20,Fhas also declined to comment further.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
