PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1780873386
OL,3,CContract signed with construction
OL,4,Cgiant to build Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FBouygues UK is a subsidiary of the
OL,7,FFrench company Bouygues Construction
OL,8,Fand has worked on more than 400
OL,9,Fhealthcare facilities worldwide,
OL,10,Fincluding hospitals in Barnet and
OL,11,FBroomfield.
OL,13,FThe UK arm has lost a total of #136
OL,14,Fmillion since 2022, but Deputy Binet
OL,15,Fpreviously defended the decision to
OL,16,Fmake them the preferred partner -
OL,17,Freferencing cash injections from their
OL,18,Fparent firm and stating that it is "a
OL,19,Fperfectly good company working in a
OL,20,Fvery difficult territory".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
