OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1780873386
OL,3,CContract signed with construction
OL,4,Cgiant to build Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FSeveral plans have been proposed over
OL,7,Fthe course of the last 15 years - the
OL,8,Fcurrent iteration was signed off by
OL,9,Fthe Planning Committee in February
OL,10,F2025.
OL,12,FHowever, without a contractor
OL,13,Fconfirmed, concerns had been raised
OL,14,Fthat any future government could
OL,15,Ffurther review and delay the project -
OL,16,Fwith Deputy Binet stating in April
OL,17,Fthat there was "no guarantee" a deal
OL,18,Fwould be agreed before the election.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
