OL,3,CContract signed with construction
OL,4,Cgiant to build Jersey's new hospital
OL,6,FFollowing this announcement,
OL,7,Fgovernment officials say they "look
OL,8,Fforward to continuing our work with
OL,9,FBouygues UK to deliver this much-
OL,10,Fneeded facility for Jersey", while
OL,11,F"further information will be issued in
OL,12,Fdue course".
OL,14,FHospital construction timeline:
